<varlistentry id="options.Handles">
      <term><emphasis remap='I'>Handles</emphasis></term>
      <listitem>
<para>Specifies that the app window will display the "low bar" decoration.
This also removes the ability to resize windows with the resize handles on
the "low bar" ends.  The is the default for all windows.</para>
      </listitem>
</varlistentry>
